a pleasent kopitiam style resturant ... offering lots of heritage dishes ...
we had the chicken curry chee cheong fun & the moonlight hor fun ...
unfurtunately the chicken curry was overly salted for my taste , while the horfun , lacked salt ... perhaps one off , off-day for the cook ...
